# Decision Capture

At session end, file significant findings to the wiki when the session produced:

- A resolved architectural ambiguity
- A bug root cause likely to recur
- A repeatable workflow that worked
- Resolution of an open question in `synthesis/OPEN_QUESTIONS.md`

Skip for routine edits (config tweaks, log review, single-file fixes).

## Direct Wiki Update

| Finding | Target file |
|---------|-------------|
| Recurring bug pattern | `synthesis/ERROR_REFERENCE.md` |
| Architectural decision | `synthesis/CAUSAL_MAP.md` |
| Resolved question | `synthesis/OPEN_QUESTIONS.md` (mark resolved) |
| New constraint | `synthesis/RULES_DRAFT.md` |
| New workflow | `synthesis/SKILLS_DRAFT.md` |

Tag provenance: `> Filed from session {uuid8} — {YYYY-MM-DD}`

Full session archival happens automatically via the ingest pipeline — no manual extract needed for routine sessions.
